SurfaceFlinger -> Overlay -> Hardware Composer -> gralloc

vendor/nvidia/tegra/hal/hwcomposer (作兩個動作 hwc_prepare, hwc_set)

HWC will base on application layer status to select HDMI mode and its resolution

MHL 是否跳進 BLIT mode (hwcomposer)
	get_hdmi_mode
	get_display_mode


Gralloc
	framebuffer device
		update screen
		detect HDMI by uevent
	allocate device
		manage native graphic buffer

hwcomposer 播放的時候都會透過gr去設定解析度, gralloc 只有差拔時候設定
